OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a bright, sunny start,
OL,6,Fcloud will increase through the
OL,7,Fmorning. Showers move in from the
OL,8,Fnorth during the afternoon, clearing
OL,9,Finto the evening. Breezy, particularly
OL,10,Fon coasts, where there will be cooler
OL,11,Ffeel to the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy during the evening
OL,14,Fwith clear spells then developing into
OL,15,Fthe night. Largely dry overnight,
OL,16,Faside from isolated coastal showers.
OL,17,FFeeling cool with a frost developing
OL,18,Fin prone rural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
