OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAfter a chilly start, sunny
OL,6,Fspells develop through the day.
OL,7,FLargely dry, cooler than recent days,
OL,8,Fwith occasional coastal showers
OL,9,Fpossible. Light winds, with a frosty
OL,10,Fnight to come.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FThursday brings sunny spells and the
OL,14,Fodd shower. Conditions turn more
OL,15,Funsettled Friday and Saturday with
OL,16,Fspells of rain or showers,
OL,17,Foccasionally heavy. At times cool,
OL,18,Fwith isolated frosts overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
